data.title: Secretary Cohen meets with Croatian President Mesic and Prime Minister Racan in the Pentagon.
data.text: Secretary of Defense William S. Cohen (2nd from right) meets with Croatian President Stjepan Mesic (left foreground) and Prime Minister Ivica Racan (right foreground) in the Pentagon on Aug. 8, 2000. Also participating on the U.S. side are Principal Deputy Under Secretary of Defense (Policy) James Bodner (far left), Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Gen. Henry H. Shelton (2nd from left), U.S. Army, and U.S. Ambassador to Croatia William D. Montgomery (right).
